---

const coreFrontend = ["React", "Vue.js", "Astro", "TypeScript", "Next.js", "Tailwind v4"];
const backendTooling = ["Go (Gin/GORM)", "Node.js", "Nestjs", "Supabase", "REST APIs"];
---

<section id="skills" class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="space-y-12">
    <!-- Encabezado -->
    <div class="space-y-2">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[--color-accent] flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[--color-accent]"></span> Stack & Infraestructura
      </h2>
      <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-white">
        Herramientas de <span class="text-gray-500">Ingeniería</span>
      </h3>
    </div>

    <!-- Bento Grid Container -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 auto-rows-[160px]">
      
      <!-- Caja 1: Core Frontend (Grande - Ocupa 2 columnas y 2 filas) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-zinc-950/40 backdrop-blur-md p-6 flex flex-col justify-between relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-[--color-accent]/20 transition-all duration-500">
        <div class="absolute -right-12 -bottom-12 h-48 w-48 rounded-full bg-[--color-accent]/5 blur-3xl group-hover:bg-[--color-accent]/10 transition-colors duration-500"></div>
        <div class="space-y-2 z-10">
          <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[--color-accent] bg-[--color-accent]/5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-[--color-accent]/10">Especialidad</span>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white pt-1">Core Frontend Architectures</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 max-w-md leading-relaxed">Desarrollo de interfaces modulares de alto rendimiento, obsesionado con los Core Web Vitals, sistemas de diseño escalables y renderizado híbrido.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 z-10 pt-4">
          {coreFrontend.map(tech => (
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-white bg-white/5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 group-hover:border-white/10 transition-colors">{tech}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Caja 2: Backend & Base de Datos (Ocupa 1 columna y 2 filas) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-1 md:row-span-2 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-zinc-950/40 backdrop-blur-md p-6 flex flex-col justify-between relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-[--color-accent]/20 transition-all duration-500">
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 bg-white/5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Capabilities</span>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white pt-1">Fullstack Mindset</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Construcción de APIs robustas y modelado de bases de datos relacionales eficientes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2 pt-4">
          {backendTooling.map(tech => (
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-xs text-gray-300">
              <span class="text-[--color-accent]">⚡</span> {tech}
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Caja 3: Control de Entorno / Setup (Ocupa 1 columna y 1 fila) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-1 md:row-span-1 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-zinc-950/40 backdrop-blur-md p-5 flex flex-col justify-between group hover:border-[--color-accent]/20 transition-all duration-500">
        <h4 class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500">Dev Environment</h4>
        <div class="space-y-1">
          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-white font-mono">Windows Terminal</p>
          <p class="text-[11px] text-gray-400 font-sans">VS Code / Git Workflows</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Caja 4: Filosofía de Ingeniería (Ocupa 2 columnas y 1 fila) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 md:row-span-1 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-zinc-950/40 backdrop-blur-md p-5 flex flex-col justify-between relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-[--color-accent]/20 transition-all duration-500">
        <div class="absolute -left-12 -top-12 h-32 w-32 rounded-full bg-[--color-accent]/5 blur-2xl"></div>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-4 w-full z-10">
          <div class="space-y-1">
            <h4 class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500">Engineering Philosophy</h4>
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-white">Clean Code & Data-Driven Solutions</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 font-mono text-[11px] text-gray-400">
            <div><span class="text-white font-bold">01/</span> Performance First</div>
            <div><span class="text-white font-bold">02/</span> Accessibility</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-gray-500 italic max-w-xl z-10">
          "El software de calidad no solo resuelve problemas técnicos actuales, sino que está diseñado para no ser una carga de mantenimiento en el futuro."
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>